Package: harmony
Title: Fast, sensitive, and accurate integration of single cell data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Korsunsky", "Ilya", email = "ilya.korsunsky@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Ilya Korsunsky <ilya.korsunsky@gmail.com>
Description: Implementation of the Harmony algorithm for single cell integration, described in Korsunsky et al <doi.org/10.1101/461954>. Package includes a standalone Harmony function, interfaces to external frameworks, and utility functions to help assess performance of the integration. 
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0), 
  Rcpp, 
  magrittr, 
  glue, 
  tibble,
  dplyr, 
  tidyr,
  purrr,
  Hmisc,
  ggplot2,
  Seurat (>= 2.3),
